OL,3,CShould new drivers face tighter
OL,4,Crestrictions after 6,000 serious
OL,5,Ccrashes?
OL,7,FAlmost 30,000 people were killed or
OL,8,Fseriously injured on UK roads in 2022
OL,9,F- and a fifth of those were the result
OL,10,Fof collisions involving cars driven by
OL,11,Fa young car driver, according to the
OL,12,FDepartment for Transport.
OL,14,FYoung males aged 17 to 24 are four
OL,15,Ftimes more likely to be killed or
OL,16,Fseriously injured in a road collision
OL,17,Fthan all other drivers aged 25 or over.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/12
