OL,3,CShould new drivers face tighter
OL,4,Crestrictions after 6,000 serious
OL,5,Ccrashes?
OL,7,FBut road novices who have just passed
OL,8,Ftheir test are subject to almost all
OL,9,Fthe same rules as their more
OL,10,Fexperienced counterparts - and change
OL,11,Fis being demanded.
OL,13,FCalls are growing for the government
OL,14,Fto introduce a "graduated driving
OL,15,Flicence", which would apply tighter
OL,16,Frestrictions on all drivers with less
OL,17,Fthan six months experience.
