OL,3,CShould new drivers face tighter
OL,4,Crestrictions after 6,000 serious
OL,5,Ccrashes?
OL,7,FThe idea is being introduced to
OL,8,FParliament by Labour MP Kim Leadbeater
OL,9,Fand is backed by various road safety
OL,10,Forganisations.
OL,12,FWhy introduce new rules for new
OL,13,Fdrivers?
OL,15,FMs Leadbeater said improving road
OL,16,Fsafety in the UK has been one of her
OL,17,F"top priorities" since meeting a
OL,18,Fcampaigner whose daughter was killed
OL,19,Fin a collision.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/12
