OL,3,CShould new drivers face tighter
OL,4,Crestrictions after 6,000 serious
OL,5,Ccrashes?
OL,7,FDr Ian Greenwood lost 12-year-old
OL,8,FAlice when the car her mother was
OL,9,Fdriving was hit in 2008. The 18-year-
OL,10,Fold driver of the other car and his 16-
OL,11,Fyear-old passenger were also killed.
OL,13,FHe is far, far from alone. Just last
OL,14,Fweek teenage couple Kamile
OL,15,FVaicikonyte, 17, and her boyfriend
OL,16,FJamie Moore, 19, died in a single-
OL,17,Fvehicle crash on the A5 near Omagh, Co
OL,18,FTyrone on Tuesday.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/12
