OL,3,CShould new drivers face tighter
OL,4,Crestrictions after 6,000 serious
OL,5,Ccrashes?
OL,7,FMs Leadbeater said: "We must never
OL,8,Fforget that behind that statistic
OL,9,Fthere are thousands of lives, right
OL,10,Facross the country, grieving or going
OL,11,Fthrough unimaginable pain. Lives
OL,12,Fchanged forever and families torn
OL,13,Fapart by tragic and often avoidable
OL,14,Fcollisions."
OL,16,FShe added: "Many of us will remember
OL,17,Fbeing new drivers. The inexperience,
OL,18,Fthe lack of confidence or, sometimes,
OL,19,Fsadly often amongst younger men, the
OL,20,Foverconfidence."
