OL,3,CShould new drivers face tighter
OL,4,Crestrictions after 6,000 serious
OL,5,Ccrashes?
OL,7,FWhat would a 'graduated driving
OL,8,Flicence' be?
OL,10,FMs Leadbeater's plan is not fully
OL,11,Fformulated and, if it were to progress
OL,12,Fthrough Parliament, would go through
OL,13,Fseveral stages of consultation and
OL,14,Fdebate before becoming law.
OL,16,FProposals already being suggested
OL,17,Finclude a ban on carrying passengers
OL,18,Funder age 25 for the first six months,
OL,19,Fand a zero alcohol limit.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/12
