OL,3,CShould new drivers face tighter
OL,4,Crestrictions after 6,000 serious
OL,5,Ccrashes?
OL,7,FRestricted passenger numbers have also
OL,8,Fbeen floated as an idea, as well as
OL,9,Flower speed limits and smaller engines
OL,10,Ffor younger drivers.
OL,12,FCurfews could ban younger motorists
OL,13,Ffrom being on certain roads at certain
OL,14,Ftimes, and P plates to show someone
OL,15,Fhas just passed could also be enforced
OL,16,Ffor six months.
OL,18,FMs Leadbeater said similar proposals
OL,19,Fhave been successfully implemented in
OL,20,Fother countries such as New Zealand.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/12
