OL,3,CShould new drivers face tighter
OL,4,Crestrictions after 6,000 serious
OL,5,Ccrashes?
OL,7,FThe graduated driving licence scheme
OL,8,Fthere has reportedly led to a 23%
OL,9,Freduction in car collision injuries
OL,10,Ffor 15`19 year olds, and a 12%
OL,11,Freduction for 20`24 year olds.
OL,13,FRAC road safety spokesperson Rod
OL,14,FDennis said: "The tragic statistics
OL,15,Fspeak for themselves.
OL,17,F"Young drivers, especially men, are
OL,18,Ffar more likely to be killed or
OL,19,Fseriously injured on our roads, so
OL,20,Fit's high time a renewed focus was
OL,21,Fgiven to reducing casualties.
